# Stream Reports

Stream Reports allows you to generate beautiful visuals of your logged-in user activity data that is captured by Stream.

**Contributors:** [x-team](http://profiles.wordpress.org/x-team), [jonathanbardo](http://profiles.wordpress.org/jonathanbardo), [bordoni](http://profiles.wordpress.org/bordoni), [shadyvb](http://profiles.wordpress.org/shadyvb), [fjarrett](http://profiles.wordpress.org/fjarrett)
